features.name: Low End PC Mode
features.description:
Select this mode as a last resort.

This option will provide you with a less than optimal experience. Do NOT enable this option if you can run the game with the default settings.

If your computer is not able to run Minecraft: Forbidden Adventures well, select this option to download a low performance variant of the game's resources.

Visit the Minecraft: Forbidden Adventures wiki for installation instructions.
